org.largecollections
Class WriteOnceReadManyArrayList<V>

java.lang.Object
  org.largecollections.WriteOnceReadManyArrayList<V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Closeable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<V>, java.util.Collection<V>, java.util.List<V>
public class WriteOnceReadManyArrayList<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<V>, java.io.Serializable, java.io.Closeable

WriteOnceReadManyArrayList is an implementation of java.util.List. It allows you to write once and read many times. An element can be added to the list but cannot be removed.
